entries.s_32: You're here with the medical supplies? Thank the Force! Our supply bag was stolen. If we saw any action, we'd have been in trouble without those supplies. Hand them to me.
entries.s_34: Unless you're here to relieve one of my guards, I'll have to ask you to loiter somewhere else.
